        "html": "<h2>Built to Last</h2>\n\n<p>DNC Direct coveralls and overalls are crafted from robust, tear-resistant materials to withstand the toughest working conditions. Reinforced stitching and heavy-duty zippers ensure these garments are built to last, offering long-lasting durability and reliability. When you choose DNC Direct, you’re investing in workwear that can handle the demands of your job.</p>\n\n<h2>Ultimate Comfort</h2>\n\n<p>Stay comfortable throughout your workday with our ergonomically designed coveralls and overalls. Featuring breathable, moisture-wicking fabrics, these garments keep you cool and dry, even during strenuous tasks. The relaxed fit and adjustable features ensure ease of movement and all-day comfort, allowing you to focus on your work without distraction.</p>\n\n<h2>Practical and Functional Design</h2>\n\n<p>Our collection includes a variety of styles with practical features such as multiple pockets, tool loops, and easy-access zippers. These functional elements provide ample storage for tools and essentials, making our coveralls and overalls as practical as they are protective. The thoughtful design ensures you have everything you need within reach, enhancing your efficiency on the job.</p>\n\n<h2>Trusted Quality</h2>\n\n<p>At DNC Direct, we prioritise quality and dependability. Our coveralls and overalls undergo rigorous testing to meet and exceed Australian safety and durability standards. When you choose DNC Coveralls and Overalls, you are choosing garments that deliver exceptional performance and reliability.</p>\n\n<span id=\"dots\">...</span><span id=\"more\">\n\n<h2>Excellent Value</h2>\n\n<p>We believe that high-quality workwear should be accessible to everyone. Our collection offers a variety of styles and sizes to fit every need and budget. Each piece is meticulously crafted to provide outstanding value, combining durability, comfort, and functionality. Investing in DNC Coveralls and Overalls is a smart choice for your work wardrobe.</p>  \n\n<h2>Versatile for All Industries</h2>\n\n<p>Our coveralls and overalls are versatile enough to meet the demands of various industries. From heavy-duty construction and manufacturing to detailed automotive work, our garments provide the perfect blend of protection and practicality. Our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction ensures you can trust DNC Direct for all your workwear needs.</p> \n\n<h2>Shop with Confidence</h2>\n\n<p>Explore the DNC Direct Coveralls and Overalls Collection today and experience the ultimate in full-body protection, durability, and comfort. Shop with confidence, knowing that you are supporting a 100% Australian owned business dedicated to delivering the best workwear on the market. Join the DNC Direct family and step into a world of quality, reliability, and superior protection.</p> \n  \n<h2>Features and Benefits</h2>\n\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n<strong>Full-Body Coverage:</strong> Provides comprehensive protection against dirt, grime, and hazardous materials.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Durable Materials:</strong> Made from tear-resistant fabrics with reinforced stitching.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Breathable and Moisture-Wicking:</strong> Keeps you cool and dry during strenuous tasks.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Practical Design:</strong> Includes multiple pockets, tool loops, and easy-access zippers for convenience.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Adjustable Fit:</strong> Ensures comfort and ease of movement.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Meets Australian Standards:</strong> Guarantees top-level quality and protection.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What sizes are available in the DNC Direct Coveralls and Overalls Collection?</strong></p>\n<p>A: We offer a wide range of sizes to ensure a perfect fit for everyone. Please refer to our size guide for detailed measurements.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Are DNC Coveralls and Overalls suitable for heavy-duty work?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Absolutely. Our coveralls and overalls are designed to provide durability and protection, making them ideal for heavy-duty work and industrial environments.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: How should I care for my coveralls and overalls?</strong></p>\n<p>A: To maintain their quality, wash your garments in cold water with mild detergent and hang them to dry. Avoid using bleach or fabric softeners. You may refer to this link on how to clean and maintain your DNC overall workwear.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What is the return policy for DNC Coveralls and Overalls?</strong></p>\n<p>A: With DNC Direct you have up to 60 days to return or exchange an unworn item.</p>\n\n<p><strong>We are unable to refund/exchange decorated items. You may refer to this link to our Returns and Exchange Policy.</strong></p>\n\n</span>\n\n<strong><button onclick=\"myFunction()\" id=\"myBtn\">Read more</button></strong>\n\n<style>\n#more {display: none;}\n</style>\n\n\n<script>\nfunction myFunction() {\n  var dots = document.getElementById(\"dots\");\n  var moreText = document.getElementById(\"more\");\n  var btnText = document.getElementById(\"myBtn\");\n\n  if (dots.style.display === \"none\") {\n    dots.style.display = \"inline\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read more\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"none\";\n  } else {\n    dots.style.display = \"none\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read less\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"inline\";\n  }\n}\n</script>"
